    Objective of Proposed Research and Background Information

My objective through this Research is to utilize data exploration to gain comprehensive ideas about the data as well as the general percentage of some particular aspect like gender and season and the mean of value of some column to have a comprehensive picture of how and which direction and methodlogy I should utilize to retrieve and analyze data. I would select the age and weight colums to have a glance of their correlation then I will go deeper to the series part where I would use specific filtering and retrieving tools in R to define the correlation of different aspect in coherant with the Medal achievement.

Kellog's vission is: "Enrich & delight the world through foods and brands that matter". And its tagline is:"Let's make today great". Hence, through Kellog's vision and tagline, it is noticable to define the potential direction for target and segmentation of Kellogg's which targets on young people or millennials with high demand of energy and full nutritient breakfast and snacks for a busy working or studying day. Hence, in overall, I would like to pay my attention on these five typical columns for which I think could be helpful for Kellog's in term of finding the right athletes to sponsor. First of all, the "Name" column should be specified, name comes with reputation and imagination, which affects significantly the brandname. Secondly, age should be focused since fact has their own that "Age" is significantly affects the brand and its target segmentation; we also look into how well ages varies in term of Olympic history. Team and Year are also important since it define place and time, where we could find the frequencies and relevant of the informations. Finally, we should also concentrate on "Medal" column where represent the acomplishment and affection of a brandname.

In stead of focusing on all age group, I will pay more attention on young age group which represent youth and capabilityWhich is suitable with Kellog's brand and product lines. Kellog's product is lean into nutrient food for breakast with convienient and lively designs Which are suitable with young and potential athletes in order to deliver these messages. Hence,instead of selecting the old age group, I will pay more attention on the younger ones and evaluate their performance throughout the Olympic history. I will also focus on the most current 10 years for the validity and the current trend of the information which can help me predict the trend for the upcoming Olympic season. Especially, Kellog's has its headquarter in United States, China, Great Britian, Mexico and Ireland so my direction is to focus on these countries while conducting analyzation. We could predict the success of certain athletes based on their performance throughout history and countries where they came from.
